# Phase 6 — versioned hook history.
#
# Lists sha256 hashes of every Genesis hook version that's been shipped.
# scripts/hooks/sync-hooks.sh uses this to distinguish "stale Genesis
# install that needs updating" (hash is a known prior version → safe to
# overwrite) from "user-modified hook" (unknown hash → leave alone).
#
# Format: <hook-name>:<sha256>
#
# Release discipline: every commit that touches scripts/hooks/{post-commit,
# pre-commit, pre-push} MUST also append the new hash to this file.
# Enforced by scripts/check_hook_versions.sh run from pre-commit.
#
# To regenerate entries for the current tree:
#   scripts/update_hook_versions.sh

